sec.p:
We sourced monthly time series from 1950 to 2014 from the Center Research Unit (CRU V3.23; 
  https://crudata.uea.ac.uk/cru/data/hrg/) at a 0.5° resolution for air temperature (AT) and from the Met Office Hadley Center (HadISST; 
  http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/hadobs/hadisst/) at a 1° resolution for sea surface temperature (SST). These raster maps are composed of 67325 and 32619 monthly observations time series for AT and SST, respectively. The number reported for the latter excludes pixels that were mostly composed of ice as those pixels are not temperature time series and can’t be analyzed with EWIs.
